spec_data.Name: jtype
spec_data.Description:
Java 5 introduced a richer type system for generics with Type and its various
sub-types, but lacks any easy way to perform common operations on these types.
JType aims to fill this gap.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 07:48:57 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A small library for working with the Java 5 type system
